Goodbye 2022 🥂 This was one of my most fruitful years yet. I am grateful to have partnered with brands, influencers, and friends on creating content they love and helping curate a brand that fits each different persons goal and dream. I am also grateful for some of the musical opportunities and TV opportunities that I was able to be a part of. Thanks to everyone who was a part of this years magic, especially the love of my life @managerdillon ❤️ Cheers to a healthy year with many blessings. Can’t wait for 2023 🎉

My New Years Resolution is to be the love someone needs and to be surrounded by the love I need.  None of that fancy diet stuff, nothing that costs even a dime… just to be the love and receive the love. It’s easy to get caught up in our own lives, jobs, desires, etc… but I really want to make this year a year of good old fashioned Christ like love. Happy New Year! 🥂
I’ll be cleaning up bottles with you on New Years Day… 🪩✨
